#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:4
msgid "Crashes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:6
msgid "The most common causes of Blender crashes."
msgstr "Die wichtigste Gründe aus denen Blender abstürzt."

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:8
msgid "Running out of memory."
msgstr "Blender geht der Speicher aus."

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:9
msgid "Issues with graphics hardware/drivers."
msgstr "Probleme mit Grafikkartenhardware oder -treibern."

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:10
msgid "Bugs in Blender."
msgstr "Fehler in Blender."

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:13
msgid ""
"Firstly, you may be able to recover your work with :menuselection:`File "
"--> Recover Last Session`."
msgstr ""
"Als erstes können Sie Ihre Arbeit vielleicht mit :menuselection:`File -->"
" Recover Last Session` wiederherstellen."

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:15
msgid ""
"To prevent the problem from happening again, you can check that the "
"graphics drivers are up to date, upgrade your machine's hardware (the RAM"
" or graphics card), and disable some options that are more memory "
"intensive:"
msgstr ""
"Um das Wiederauftreten des Problems zu verhindern, können Sie "
"kontrollieren, dass die Grafikkartentreiber aktuell sind, Ihren Computer "
"aufrüsten (den Arbeitsspeicher oder die Grafikkarte) und einige Optionen "
"deaktivieren, die mehr Speicher verbrauchen:"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:18
msgid ""
"Reduce undo steps :menuselection:`User Preferences --> Editing --> Undo "
"Steps`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:20
msgid ""
"Disable *Region Overlap* and *Triple buffering* at :menuselection:`User "
"Preferences --> System --> Window Draw Method`."
msgstr ""
"Deaktivieren Sie *Region Overlap* und *Triple buffering* in "
":menuselection:`User Preferences --> System --> Window Draw Method`."

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:22
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Using multisample, anti-aliasing also increases the memory usage and make"
" display slower."
msgstr ""
"Die Benutzung von multisample und anti-aliasing erhöht ebenfalls den "
"Speicherverbrauch und macht die Anzeige langsamer."

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:23
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"On Linux, the Window Manager (KDE, Gnome, Unity) may be using hardware "
"accelerated effects (eg. window shadows and transparency) that are using "
"up the memory that Blender needs. Try disabling the desktop effects or "
"switch to a lightweight Window Manager."
msgstr ""
"Auf Linux benutzt der Fenstermanager (KDE, Gnome, Unity) eventuell "
"Hardware-beschleunigte Effekte (z. B. Schatten und Transparenz), die den "
"Speicher aufbrauchen, den Blender benötigt. Versuchen Sie die Effekte "
"abzustellen oder wechseln Sie zu einem leichtgewichtigeren "
"Fenstermanager."

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:29
msgid "Crash Log"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:31
msgid ""
"When Blender crashes it writes out a text file which contains "
"informations that may help identify the cause of the crash."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:34
msgid ""
"On a crash, a file is written based on the name of the currently loaded "
"blend file, so ``test.blend`` will create a file called "
"``test.crash.txt``. The crash log for unsaved files will be written into "
"the :ref:`temp-dir` directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:38
msgid ""
"This file contains a log of tools used up until the crash as well as some"
" other debug information."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:40
msgid ""
"When reporting bugs on crashes it can be helpful to attach this file to "
"your reports, especially when others are unable to reproduce the crash."
msgstr ""

